      "name": "Tips To Follow",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "What Are the Best Jewelry Care Tips to Follow ?",
        "paragraph1": "<p>Ever noticed how some jewelry catches the light effortlessly, turning heads without even trying? That kind of brilliance doesn’t just last on its own, it stays because of true quality and the care that keeps it shining. We, at Lucira, craft your jewelry with the finest materials and design our pieces to last for lifetimes but even the best jewelry needs a little attention, love and care to maintain its brilliance.</p>",
        "paragraph2": "<p>Keep your jewelry shining with everyday care tips, smart storage ideas, and simple solutions for knots and tangles. This guide helps you care for your diamond jewelry with the attention it truly deserves.</p>",
