      "name": "Tips Image With Text",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Daily Jewelry Care Tips",
        "sub_heading": "A little care goes a long way in keeping your jewelry radiant.",
        "paragraph": "<ul><li> Put your jewelry on after makeup, perfume, and lotion, let it be the final touch. </li><li>Take it off before bedtime to prevent any damage.</li><li>Avoid wearing solitaires while swimming or exercising, as sweat and chlorine can dull the sparkle. Bezel-set pieces, however, are perfectly safe for active wear and you can always add our Ring Shield for extra protection.</li><li>Keep jewelry away from harsh chemicals, they can fade its shine and loosen its setting                              over time.<br/></li></ul>",
